20, 30 men.

56
00:03:02,967 --> 00:03:04,801
That's funny.

57
00:03:04,836 --> 00:03:06,052
What is?

58
00:03:06,087 --> 00:03:07,303
Well, i know
i heard horses,

59
00:03:07,338 --> 00:03:09,189
