150
00:09:19,642 --> 00:09:24,013
I don't understand.

151
00:09:24,048 --> 00:09:27,149
I just don't understand.

152
00:09:27,184 --> 00:09:29,652
What's happened to you?

153
00:09:30,269 --> 00:09:31,520
Why are you...

154
00:09:31,555 --> 00:09:34,023
