155
00:09:34,058 --> 00:09:37,159
None of you can speak?

156
00:09:37,194 --> 00:09:40,279
None of you can move.

157
00:10:01,183 --> 00:10:04,303
First meat i've had
in a couple of months, you hear?

158
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:32,581
Wind... must be the wind.

159
