I done that, you know.

180
00:12:09,263 --> 00:12:11,847
Put them all to sleep.

181
00:12:11,882 --> 00:12:16,235
You don't believe
me, do you?

182
00:12:16,270 --> 00:12:17,486
You think i'm lying.

183
00:12:17,521 --> 00:12:19,989
I ain't
called you no liar.

184
