stands the enemy?

201
00:13:07,071 --> 00:13:08,904
Not even a twitch?

202
00:13:08,939 --> 00:13:12,041
Not even a move
in the eyeball?

203
00:13:12,076 --> 00:13:13,909
Well!

204
00:13:17,081 --> 00:13:19,548
"Ye soldier, conjured here

205
