now, listen, old man...!

208
00:13:27,091 --> 00:13:30,810
How 'bout it now, johnny reb?

209
00:13:30,845 --> 00:13:31,427
You believe me?

210
00:13:31,462 --> 00:13:33,312
I reckon you
believe me now

211
00:13:33,347 --> 00:13:35,815
